All sales are in U.S. Currency. Shipping Terms:

Shipping costs are based on books weighing 1.0 LBS. If your book order is heavy or oversized, we may contact you to let you know extra shipping is required. Hawai orders will take 21-36 days to arrive with free shipping. If you are interested in a faster delivery choose the express option. Orders from Alaska can't meet the current shipping speed deadline (normally it takes 3 weeks or more to ship an item from the continental USA). If a buyer from Alaska or Hawai wants the item sooner they have to choose the priority option. We might require additional shipping charges for orders shipped to Hawai or Alaska. WE SHIP ALL DOMESTIC ORDERS WITH A DELIVERY SIGNATURE!!!
